===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/saɪdwɔːk/|lang=en}}
* {{audio|en-us-sidewalk.ogg|Audio (US)|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{label|en|US}} A [[footpath]], usually [[pave]]d, at the side of a [[road]] for the use of [[pedestrian]]s; a [[pavement]] {{qualifier|UK}} or footpath {{qualifier|Australia}}; by extension, any paved footpath, even if not located at the side of a road.

